      <layout-options>
        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>1. Implement the Dashboard Across Teams</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Share the dashboard with Operations, Logistics, Merchandising, and Customer Support.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Train teams on how to use filters to identify root causes.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Schedule weekly reviews of return trends.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>2. Launch Targeted Quality Improvements</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Prioritize fixes for high‑return sub‑categories.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Work with suppliers to address product defects.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Update product descriptions and images to reduce mismatches.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>3. Improve Customer Experience</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Reach out to customers with unusually high return rates.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Provide better pre‑purchase guidance for high‑risk products.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Offer proactive support during seasonal spikes.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>4. Strengthen Operational Processes</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Audit shipping accuracy and packaging quality.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Reduce transit damage by optimizing warehouse handling.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Track supplier‑level return rates and renegotiate terms.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>5. Monitor Key Metrics Over Time</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Review return rate by category, geography, and customer segment monthly.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Investigate outliers immediately.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Use the dashboard to validate whether interventions are working.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>6. Plan for Long‑Term Improvements</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Integrate return data into forecasting and inventory planning.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Build automated alerts for unusual return patterns.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Continue refining the dashboard based on stakeholder feedback.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </caption>
      </layout-options>
